# Keep build context small + reproducible. Source is copied explicitly in the Dockerfiles;
# never ship local installs, build output, secrets, or VCS metadata into an image.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/playwright-report
**/test-results
.git
.github
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.log
legacy_inventory
docs
**/*.md
!apps/api/README.md
!apps/web/README.md
